Hi Mike.  First off I&#39;m not experienced in the least!!  I have been doing
this for about 1 MONTH.  :-)



One of my first sessions I was really trying hard to hear from my niece and
nephew who passed in Nov of 07 in a car accident.  I had what I considered
to be some responses from spirit about them.  



I have the clips at ESNIPS:  

http://www.esnips.com/doc/60ad1c13-cb94-4591-8ec1-db61132a1349/DO-NOT-WOORY-
ABOUT-CHILD-DO-NOT-CRY-ITS-ME-THEYRE-DOIN-FANTASTIC



and..



http://www.esnips.com/doc/91baf9f8-84af-4c76-b3d0-2c1294d514c3/WAKE-UP-MY-SI
STER-or-SYSTEM-AT-NIGHT



The first one IS ROUGH and I hadn&#39;t learned how to edit the files down.  But
it said DO NOT WORRY ABOUT CHILD - DO NOT CRY - THEY&#39;RE DOIN FANSTATIC.  The
&quot;They&#39;re doing fantastic&quot; sounds like a Scottish/Irish accent.  My sister
married an Englishman with relatives in Scotland and Ireland and Wales.  The
second clip didn&#39;t make any sense to me. WAKE UP MY SISTER AT NITE (or
system).  



The answer to your question about sharing these with a relative was one I
contemplated for awhile.  The loss is so raw for my sister - she lost her
two of her children.  But I decided to share it.  When I first told her
about the WAKE UP MY SISTER one I didn&#39;t know if it would mean anything to
her but she said it meant a lot.  She has a surviving daughter - Emma age 10
left who apparently was being woken up in the middle of the night claiming
that her brother was waking her up and bothering her.



My sister really hasn&#39;t commented on the clips and I haven&#39;t bugged her. I
only hope it helped her and not caused her any undue pain.  

I will try and find out what she thinks and get back to you when she decides
to talk about the clips.



Kristin



  _____  

From: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com [mailto:EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com] On Behalf Of
Michael Edwards
Sent: Wednesday, March 26, 2008 8:35 AM
To: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com
Subject: Re: [EVP-ITC] Re: New file uploaded to EVP-ITC



Hi Steve, hope all is well with you.



From this site it appears that yourself, Frank, Bruce, and Kristin and
others I can not think of at the moment, have been engaged in contact as
such that you ask a question and they give an answer. Have any of you ever
taken the info you receive from lets say one spirit and tried to contact
their living relative to give them a copy of the recording? Have spirits
asked you more experienced researchers to do that, and if so, was the person
you contacted indeed the correct loved one, and what was their response in
you contacting them?  I think this would be awesome to be able to serve as a
messenger to the deceased



Mike Edwards Cary NC

Steve Hultay &lt;urkel23@...&gt; wrote:

I heard &quot;Help&quot; twice and than &quot;Lord&quot;. The second &quot;help&quot; is in the 
static white noise area after the first really clear one.

-Steve H.

--- In EVP-ITC@yahoogroups &lt;mailto:EVP-ITC%40yahoogroups.com&gt; .com,
